OL,7,FThe head of the Post Office has said
OL,8,Fhe would uphold over half of
OL,9,Fprosecutions of sub-postmasters
OL,10,Fconvicted under the scandal, in a
OL,11,Fletter to the justice secretary.
OL,13,FChief Executive Nick Read said the
OL,14,FPost Office would be "bound to oppose
OL,15,Fan appeal" in at least 369 of the 700
OL,16,Fcases it had prosecuted.
