OL,7,FMr Read's letter, sent shortly after
OL,8,Fthe ITV drama sparked public outrage,
OL,9,Fsaid the cases "involve convictions
OL,10,Fobtained by reliance on evidence
OL,11,Funrelated to the Horizon computer
OL,12,Fsystem" and represented a "much more
OL,13,Fsignificant" proportion of the
OL,14,Fprosecutions than those the company
OL,15,Fwas likely to concede in court.
OL,17,FIt comes after the minister for the
OL,18,FPost Office admitted will also clear
OL,19,Fthe names of people "who were, in
OL,20,Ffact, guilty of a crime".
