OL,8,Fin the 369 cases "clearly raises acute
OL,9,Fpolitical, judicial and communications
OL,10,Fchallenges against the very
OL,11,Fsignificant public and parliamentary
OL,12,Fpressure for some form of acceleration
OL,13,For bypassing of the normal appeals
OL,14,Fprocess".
OL,16,FIn an attached note from lawyers
