OL,7,FWhen asked about the letter on Friday,
OL,8,Fthe prime minister's spokesperson said
OL,9,Fthe government remains "undeterred" in
OL,10,Fplans to quash the convictions of
OL,11,Fwronged sub-postmasters.
OL,13,F"We think it's right that we take what
OL,14,Fis an extraordinary step to overturn
OL,15,Fconvictions.
OL,17,F"This was one of the greatest
OL,18,Fmiscarriages of justice in our
OL,19,Fnation's history, so we continue to
OL,20,Fwork to deliver that swiftly", the
OL,21,Fspokesman said.
